{"file_name": "ETC_multipage.pdf", "file_type": "pdf", "confidence": 0.79, "time_taken": 2.98, "memory_mb": 6.48, "units": [{"index": 1, "method": "structured", "confidence": 0.79, "text": {"text": "VIKRAM SINGH\nSenior Management Consultant\nBengaluru, India | vikram.singh@email.com | +91-9XXXXXXXXX\nPROFESSIONAL SUMMARY\nSenior Consultant with over 15 years of experience delivering strategic, operational, and digital transformation\ninitiatives across banking, technology, manufacturing, and professional services sectors. Proven ability to lead\nlarge-scale consulting engagements, advise C-level stakeholders, and drive measurable business outcomes.\nStrong expertise in business strategy, process optimization, data-driven decision-making, and change\nmanagement.\nCORE CONSULTING EXPERTISE\n(cid:127) Business & Corporate Strategy\n(cid:127) Digital Transformation & Process Reengineering\n(cid:127) Operating Model Design\n(cid:127) Program & Change Management\n(cid:127) Data Analytics & Performance Management\n(cid:127) Stakeholder & Executive Advisory\n(cid:127) Financial Modeling & Business Case Development\nPROFESSIONAL EXPERIENCE\nSenior Consultant \u2013 Alpha Consulting Group (2016 \u2013 Present)\n(cid:127) Lead multi-disciplinary consulting engagements for Fortune 500 and mid-sized enterprises across India and\nSoutheast Asia.\n(cid:127) Advise CXOs on strategy formulation, operating model redesign, and digital transformation initiatives.\n(cid:127) Delivered transformation programs resulting in cost reductions of up to 22% and productivity improvements\nexceeding 30%.\n(cid:127) Manage project teams, budgets, timelines, and client communication to ensure successful delivery.", "tables": []}}, {"index": 2, "method": "structured", "confidence": 0.8, "text": {"text": "(cid:127) Designed enterprise-wide KPI frameworks and performance dashboards to enable data-driven decision-making\nfor senior leadership.\n(cid:127) Conducted market assessments, competitor benchmarking, and financial analysis to support strategic\ninvestment decisions.\n(cid:127) Partnered with client leadership to manage change initiatives, including communication planning and capability\nbuilding.\n(cid:127) Mentored junior consultants and analysts, providing guidance on problem-solving, client engagement, and\nprofessional development.\nConsultant \u2013 Beta Advisory Services (2010 \u2013 2016)\n(cid:127) Supported large consulting engagements focused on operational excellence, cost optimization, and process\nimprovement.\n(cid:127) Led workstreams involving business process mapping, gap analysis, and solution design across finance,\noperations, and IT functions.\n(cid:127) Developed detailed business cases, implementation roadmaps, and executive presentations for senior\nstakeholders.\n(cid:127) Collaborated closely with client teams to ensure practical and sustainable solutions were implemented.\nKEY ENGAGEMENTS\n(cid:127) Core Banking Transformation Program \u2013 Tier-1 Bank\n(cid:127) ERP Implementation & Process Redesign \u2013 Manufacturing Client\n(cid:127) Enterprise Cost Optimization \u2013 Professional Services Firm\n(cid:127) Data & Analytics Strategy \u2013 Retail Organization", "tables": []}}, {"index": 3, "method": "structured", "confidence": 0.78, "text": {"text": "EDUCATION\n(cid:127) Master of Business Administration (Strategy & Operations) \u2013 IIM Bangalore\n(cid:127) Bachelor of Engineering \u2013 Computer Science\nCERTIFICATIONS\n(cid:127) PMP \u2013 Project Management Professional\n(cid:127) Certified Management Consultant (CMC)\n(cid:127) Lean Six Sigma Black Belt\nPUBLICATIONS & THOUGHT LEADERSHIP\n(cid:127) Published articles on digital transformation and operational excellence in leading business journals.\n(cid:127) Regular speaker at industry conferences and corporate leadership forums.\nKEY ACHIEVEMENTS\n(cid:127) Successfully led consulting programs exceeding INR 100 Crores in value.\n(cid:127) Recognized as \u201cTop Performer \u2013 Consulting Excellence\u201d multiple times.\n(cid:127) Built and scaled high-performing consulting teams across regions.\nADDITIONAL INFORMATION\n(cid:127) Strong executive presence and communication skills\n(cid:127) Extensive experience working with global clients\n(cid:127) Passionate about mentoring and capability building", "tables": []}}], "error": null, "embedding": [-0.008245237171649933, -0.0002930525806732476, -0.03391212970018387, 0.011554648168385029, 0.04808078706264496, 0.0033387208823114634, 0.015675926581025124, 0.05069899931550026, -0.013451018370687962, -0.026077955961227417, -0.03326724097132683, -0.02654062584042549, -0.03670632094144821, 0.02463916875422001, 0.07380803674459457, 0.06996549665927887, 0.018025921657681465, -0.03629244491457939, 0.04851464927196503, 0.015515688806772232, -0.00033781665842980146, 0.0038842784706503153, 0.01724243350327015, 0.04756675660610199, 0.035352304577827454, -0.004810946993529797, 0.04992308095097542, -0.007674864958971739, -0.07379430532455444, -0.06727898865938187, 0.03586167097091675, -0.050136834383010864, -0.024382788687944412, -0.01173448283225298, 0.014370882883667946, -0.030109351500868797, -0.03769579902291298, -0.016410280019044876, 0.0017467645229771733, -0.05262242257595062, -0.043842464685440063, -0.02939421497285366, -0.017664602026343346, -0.02245333418250084, -0.04080624878406525, 0.0026331348344683647, -0.05602461099624634, 0.03916890174150467, -0.006738633383065462, 0.012449981644749641, -0.029477789998054504, 0.03866975009441376, -0.0131654292345047, -0.002705349586904049, 0.04113103076815605, 0.057338397949934006, 0.023109281435608864, -0.0704958364367485, -0.04738008603453636, -0.04415271803736687, 0.04260476678609848, -0.04916149377822876, 0.02095239982008934, 0.023369034752249718, 0.043626319617033005, 0.013572882860898972, 0.03760257363319397, 0.009783490560948849, -0.04966796934604645, -0.0012064711190760136, -0.06781098991632462, -0.009794599376618862, 0.02007055096328